Product Information. K-Phos Original (potassium acid phosphate)." Beach Pharmaceuticals, Tampa, FL.[4] "Product Information. Phospho-Trin 250 Neutral (potassium phosphate-sodium phosphate)." Patrin Pharma, Skokie, IL.[5] "Product Information. SSKI (potassium iodide)." Upsher-Smith Laboratories Inc, Minneapolis, MN.[6] "Product Information. Potassium Chloride (potassium chloride)." Pharmaceutical Assoc Inc Div Beach Products, Greenville, SC.', 1767369485);
